text: Jang Eu-suk is a South Korean taekwondo practitioner. She won a gold medal in finweight at the 1987 World Taekwondo Championships in Barcelona, after defeating Rosa Moreno in the semifinal, and Mónica Torres in the final. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:South Korean female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
